data.description: COUNTRY LIVING WITH ATTENTION TO DETAIL!! This upscale, gated country estate with all the comforts of home is truly one of a kind!! From the “hearth room” that features a beautiful mantle made from 100-yr-old barn beams, a gourmet kitchen, and ship-lap wall accents throughout to the den (with mountain view), an inviting master suite, and gorgeous bath… you’ll enjoy the inviting ‘down home’ space! You’ll also appreciate the fully finished basement including a second den/rec room, a full bath, and tons of storage! Equally attractive, you’ll be drawn to the unbelievable outdoor freedom with in-ground pool, beautiful barn (w/ five stables), and a perfect pasture for your horses (fenced away from the home)! This gem comes with 5.5(+/-) acres and almost 3300(+/-) sq ft of living space! Schedule a viewing today and come see it for yourself!!!
